<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <span class="header-label">Apothena Career Services — Internal Reference</span>
    <h1>Assessment <em>Debrief Guide</em></h1>
    <p class="header-sub">Coach's Reference for Interpreting Assessment Results Across All Sessions</p>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <span class="meta-pill">Part A — Career Charting</span>
      <span class="meta-pill">Part B — Education Planner</span>
