      <p>Identifies the client's core character strengths — stable, values-based qualities that feel most authentic and energizing. VIA is the only framework in Career Charting that addresses why a client works. It is particularly powerful for clients who are technically skilled but feel chronically empty. Refer every client to the full free VIA at viacharacter.org.</p>
    </div>

