      <ul class="prompt-list">
        <li>"Think of a week where you felt most like yourself professionally. What were you doing that activated this strength?"</li>
        <li>"What would your work look like if you were using this strength every single day in a way that genuinely mattered?"</li>
        <li>"Is there a role or environment from your past where this strength was actively suppressed? What was the cost of that?"</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <span class="block-label">What to Watch For</span>
      <ul class="watch-list">
        <li>High Humanity scores (Kindness, Love, Social Intelligence) in data-heavy or isolated roles almost always explain chronic dissatisfaction — even in well-compensated positions.</li>
