          <tr><td>Honesty &amp; Integrity</td><td>Programs with strong ethics components — law, medicine, journalism, public policy.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Kindness &amp; Compassion</td><td>Service-learning programs: social work, healthcare, education, community development.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Leadership &amp; Teamwork</td><td>Programs with student leadership development, real agency, and group project culture.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Creativity &amp; Originality</td><td>Studio-based, project-driven programs that reward original thinking.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Humor &amp; Gratitude</td><td>Campuses with strong community culture, extracurriculars, and genuine social warmth.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Bravery &amp; Perseverance</td><td>Rigorous, competitive programs where persistence is genuinely tested and rewarded.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prudence &amp; Self-Discipline</td><td>Self-paced, independent, or online programs that reward structure and self-management.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Purpose &amp; Spirituality</td><td>Mission-driven institutions or programs with strong connection to service and purpose.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

